# Frontend (React + Vite + pnpm)

## Layout

```
frontend/src/
  App.jsx              # router shell
  pages/Dashboard.jsx  # main dashboard, Technical Health Matrix, llms.txt block
  pages/PageDetail.jsx # deep audit signals grid
```

## Conventions

- Package manager: **pnpm** (`packageManager` pinned in `package.json`)
- Security: `.npmrc` enforces lockfile + `minimum-release-age`; never switch back to npm
- Styling: Tailwind in JSX; global styles in `index.css` / `App.css`
- API base URL is hardcoded `http://localhost:8000` (known bug — check env if fixing)

## Scripts

```bash
pnpm dev      # dev server :5173
pnpm build    # production build
pnpm lint     # eslint
pnpm format   # prettier
```

## UI ↔ API mapping

| UI area | Endpoint |
|---------|----------|
| Domain gaps | `GET /api/gaps?domain=` |
| Roadmap | `GET /api/benchmark?domain=` |
| How to Fix panel | `POST /api/generate-fix` |
| Draft Content | `POST /api/generate-content` |
| Deep audit | `POST /api/audit` |
